# EmailJS Configuration for Contact Form
# 
# To set up email functionality using EmailJS (recommended):
# 1. Go to https://www.emailjs.com and create a free account
# 2. Add an email service (Gmail, Outlook, etc.)
# 3. Create an email template
# 4. Copy your credentials below:
#
# Find these in EmailJS Dashboard:
# - Public Key: Settings → API Keys → Public Key
# - Service ID: Email Services → Select your service
# - Template ID: Email Templates → Select your template
#
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=YOUR_PUBLIC_KEY_HERE
VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=service_xxxxxxxxx
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=template_xxxxxxxxx
VITE_EMAILJS_TO_EMAIL=dovehomes247@gmail.com

